.SH NAME
pm_stay_awake \- Notify the PM core that a wakeup event is being processed.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" pm_stay_awake
.BI "(struct device *dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
Device the wakeup event is related to.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Notify the PM core of a wakeup event (signaled by \fIdev\fP) by calling
__pm_stay_awake for the \fIdev\fP's wakeup source object.

Call this function after detecting of a wakeup event if \fBpm_relax\fP is going
to be called directly after processing the event (and possibly passing it to
user space for further processing).
